annotationA: Proteasome regulator dREG; Endopeptidase activator activity; endopeptidase inhibitor activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; regulation of proteasomal protein catabolic process; regulation of G1/S transition of mitotic cell cycle
annotationB: Probable 26S proteasome non-ATPase regulatory subunit 3; Acts as a regulatory subunit of the 26 proteasome which is involved in the ATP-dependent degradation of ubiquitinated proteins
